<item>What resource or capability challenges have Uber and Lyft faced because their fast company growth?</item>
<item>What PESTEL factors do you think are contributing to the popularity of ride-sharing services?</item>
<item>What industry challenges (think of Porter’s Five Forces) does the use of self-driving cars address?</item>
